refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
resourcestream_filter_prepend resourcestream stringfiltername intread_write mixedparams
Adds filtername to the list of filters attached to stream.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns a resource which can be used to refer to this filter
 instance during a call to stream_filter_remove.

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     5.1.0

      Prior to PHP 5.1.0, this function returns &true; on success
      or &false; on failure.
